def mod ( num , a ) :					      Disassembly of <code object mod at 0x7f33e2649a50, file "<dis Disassembly of <code object mod at 0x7f816a6e4b70, file "<dis script_not_found : None

def nthRoot ( A , N ) :					      Disassembly of <code object nthRoot at 0x7f33e2644f60, file " Disassembly of <code object nthRoot at 0x7f816a6e4ae0, file " script_not_found : None
    xPre = random.randint ( 1 , 101 ) % 10		      2 0 LOAD_GLOBAL 0 ( random )				    11 0 LOAD_GLOBAL 0 ( xPre )					  
    eps = 0.001						      2 LOAD_METHOD 1 ( randint )				    2 LOAD_METHOD 1 ( randint )					  
    delX = 2147483647					      4 LOAD_CONST 1 ( 1 )					    4 LOAD_CONST 1 ( 101 )					  
    xK = 0.0						      6 LOAD_CONST 2 ( 101 )					    6 LOAD_CONST 2 ( 100 )					  
    while ( delX > eps ) :				      8 CALL_METHOD 2						    8 LOAD_CONST 3 ( 100 )					  
	xK = ( ( N - 1.0 ) * xPre + A / pow ( xPre , N - 1 )  10 LOAD_CONST 3 ( 10 )					    10 LOAD_CONST 4 ( ( 'N' , 'N' ) )				  
	delX = abs ( xK - xPre )			      12 BINARY_MODULO						    12 CALL_METHOD 4
